{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/622650/extras/Bendy_SteamGraphics_Header_DreamsComeTrue.png?t=1729706369\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/622650/extras/BATIM_SteamPageFrameGif_01.gif?t=1729706369\" /><br>Explore as Henry as he revisits the old demons of his past by travelling deep into the abandoned animation workshop of Joey Drew Studios, a studio with a dark history. With twists and turns around every corner, &quot;Bendy and the Ink Machine&quot; is sure to keep you on edge... and decimate your childhood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/622650/extras/Bendy_SteamGraphics_Header_AnimationStudio_1.png?t=1729706369\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/622650/extras/BATIM_SteamPageFrameGif_02.gif?t=1729706369\" /><br>A deeply atmospheric and spine-tingling experience with secrets hiding behind it's drawn walls and scribbled doors. Traverse into the shadows, where the monsters of the past dwell and our creations come alive.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/622650/extras/Bendy_SteamGraphics_Header_Mystery_1.png?t=1729706369\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/622650/extras/BATIM_SteamPageFrameGif_03.gif?t=1729706369\" /><br>Friends and foes will help or hinder your path as you unravel the great mystery of the studio. Whom can you trust? What horrors await your next encounter? Insanity is the name of the game down here.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/622650/extras/Bendy_SteamGraphics_Header_Horrors_1.png?t=1729706369\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/622650/extras/BATIM_SteamPageFrameGif_04.gif?t=1729706369\" /><br>The creatures of the Dark Puddles surround you as you are faced with puzzling obstacles. You're never alone. You're never safe. Your animated nightmares are just beginning.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Picking Up the Pieces","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/622650/84539f8204d46c94fccea49930ad0f145a5a8c62.jpg"},{"name":"Hello Bendy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/622650/bd59a1b0eab3b1bdc73191ba635c49b1906b403d.jpg"},{"name":"Crooner Tuner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/622650/2e8774ee104f77c3ae6bd54ff333ab32077ae66a.jpg"},{"name":"The Creator","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/622650/602fb8953bc205360ed43128be877558d40288d7.jpg"},{"name":"My Favorite Song","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/622650/5567cf785779a0f0b804579227c1f6dd48f7f9fa.jpg"},{"name":"Strike Up The Band","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/622650/7df0f708c9438df3d87d08c778b1453a402a1344.jpg"},{"name":"Coast to Coast","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/622650/82ac0cae8e0c54142f27e8a5c8e7ab0bb5047003.jpg"},{"name":"Canadian Bacon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/622650/c57472fae8e56844262178570e138b8cdaf3917c.jpg"},{"name":"The Believer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/622650/6d7066e3dba80178ad45f037fa22e9ef155efceb.jpg"},{"name":"Man Behind the Curtain","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/622650/f20012144c8bcd031a65a0cf7df92ac272d4695f.jpg"}],"total":61},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i